00:59:48,000 --> 00:59:54,440
to delight our current customers such that they 
would tell their friends. And other businesses,  

604
00:59:54,440 --> 00:59:59,600
that's always somewhat useful, but you can also 
reach people with billboards and Google ads and  

605
00:59:59,600 --> 01:00:05,040
other types of upsells. That's very difficult 
in the moment that someone is starting a company  

