625
01:02:02,503 --> 01:02:05,560
... emit the log line and count it. The 
frequencies could be kind of mind-blowing. And  

626
01:02:05,560 --> 01:02:11,120
I think for almost any scale business, if you are 
bored one day and you're not sure what to measure,  

627
01:02:11,120 --> 01:02:16,520
just make a user having a bad day chart, emit 
a log line and count it as a bar chart and then  

628
01:02:16,520 --> 01:02:24,120
