01:08:42,120 --> 01:08:48,000
system. And we have a special place called Go 
Metrics. Many people use a go/service where  

691
01:08:48,000 --> 01:08:53,480
you can just quickly go to a URL. And again, 
I have to sometimes do a rule rather than a  

